ygData.messageBody:
Last night I suffered 5 deaths in Hate. However, the very first scorn
banshee pull yielded Imbrued Legs and I won the lotto!!! WOO HOO! I
immediately saw that the stats on the spoiler sites were incorrect regarding
the AC. Did anyone ever get a list of the AC upgrades to Imbrued? Other
stats were the same so I'm assuming they just gave the armor an AC buff. If
anyone could direct me to a website or list the AC changes I'd appreciate
it.

Anthem Dirgemaker
Level 49 Bard of Qeynos Solusek Ro
Anthem
Level 2 Bard of Qeynos Inoruuk
